        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Top, tail, and finely dice your<strong> carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped onion </strong>and<strong> diced carrot </strong>and cook for 4 min or until softened</p>",
